# State & Data Fetching

## SWR (`src/app/swr/`)

- Fetcher key: `{ url, params, method? }` via `SWRProvider`
- Export hooks returning `{ data, error, isLoading, isValidating, mutate }`
- Use `useSWRImmutable` for quiz/list payloads (no auto-revalidate)
- Reference: `src/app/swr/useGrammarToday.ts`

## Zustand (`src/app/store/`)

```typescript
create<T>()(devtools(persist((set, get) => ({ ... }), { name: "featureStore" })))
```

- Hold filters (`level`, `study`), item lists, UI toggles
- List fetch via store actions calling API `fetch` when matching existing stores
- Do not duplicate metadata that already lives in SWR hooks
